OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776525067
OL,3,CManchester Piccadilly rail disruption
OL,4,Ccontinues into the weekend
OL,6,FRail passengers have been warned to
OL,7,Fplan ahead as work continues to repair
OL,8,Fdamaged overhead wires close to
OL,9,FManchester Piccadilly station.
OL,11,FWiring above the railway was damaged
OL,12,Fon Thursday morning (16 April) and
OL,13,Fengineering teams from Network Rail
OL,14,Fare continuing to repair the damaged
OL,15,Fwires.
OL,17,FTrains are now running but the company
OL,18,Fsays further repairs will need on
OL,19,FSaturday night and running until
OL,20,FSunday morning (18 and 19 April).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
