PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776525067
OL,3,CManchester Piccadilly rail disruption
OL,4,Ccontinues into the weekend
OL,6,FAn amended timetable will be in place
OL,7,Funtil 11pm on Saturday night.
OL,9,FFrom 11pm, no trains will run out of
OL,10,FManchester Piccadilly, including from
OL,11,Fplatforms 13 and 14, and an amended
OL,12,Ftimetable will be in place at other
OL,13,Fcentral Manchester stations.
OL,15,FServices into and out of Manchester
OL,16,FPiccadilly will start again at 11am on
OL,17,FSunday morning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
