PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776525067
OL,3,CManchester Piccadilly rail disruption
OL,4,Ccontinues into the weekend
OL,6,FPassengers have been urged to check
OL,7,Fwith their train operators before
OL,8,Ftravelling - particularly with big
OL,9,Fsporting events taking place,
OL,10,Fincluding the Manchester Marathon and
OL,11,FManchester City vs Arsenal on Sunday.
OL,13,FThe overhead line equipment carries
OL,14,F25,000 volts of electricity to power
OL,15,Felectric trains.
OL,17,FIt's a critical part of the railway
OL,18,Fthat allows Network Rail to run faster
OL,19,Fand greener electric services,
OL,20,Freplacing trains running on diesel,
OL,21,Fthe organisation said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
