PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776525067
OL,3,CManchester Piccadilly rail disruption
OL,4,Ccontinues into the weekend
OL,6,F"We are carrying out a full repair on
OL,7,FSaturday night. To do this, we need to
OL,8,Fclose the line into Manchester
OL,9,FPiccadilly between 11pm on Saturday
OL,10,Fand 11am on Sunday. Please, if you are
OL,11,Fplanning to travel into Manchester by
OL,12,Frail on Sunday morning, plan your
OL,13,Fjourney in advance and allow extra
OL,14,Ftravel time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
