PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776525067
OL,3,CManchester Piccadilly rail disruption
OL,4,Ccontinues into the weekend
OL,6,FSimon Turner, Head of Operational
OL,7,FReadiness at Avanti West Coast, said:
OL,8,F"We'll be operating a significantly
OL,9,Freduced timetable between Manchester
OL,10,FPiccadilly and London Euston on
OL,11,FSaturday 18 April due to the ongoing
OL,12,Fissues with the overhead electric
OL,13,Fwires. These services are expected to
OL,14,Fbe extremely busy, and we strongly
OL,15,Fadvise customers to check before they
OL,16,Ftravel.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
