PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776525067
OL,3,CManchester Piccadilly rail disruption
OL,4,Ccontinues into the weekend
OL,6,F"We're continuing to work with Network
OL,7,FRail and industry partners to help
OL,8,Fcustomers get to their destinations
OL,9,Fvia alternative routes. We'd like to
OL,10,Fthank customers for their patience and
OL,11,Fremind anyone whose journey is delayed
OL,12,Fby 15 minutes or more to claim Delay
OL,13,FRepay compensation."
OL,15,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,16,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,17,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,18,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@TO]
